posting_body: ['STRICT LIMIT OF 3 OCCUPANTS!', '(this includes both adults &children)', 'AVAILABLE for 9/1 move ins', 'This brand newly listed house is located in one of the hottest and safest neighborhoods of Minneapolis and is priced to move!', 'Located walking and biking distance to the University of Minnesota campus & a multitude of new micro breweries and taprooms.', '$1225 1st month special & $1275 regular rent your own whole single family home!', "Brand new listing so it's available for sure.", 'First appointments to tour the home will be tomorrow after 5pm.', 'For an appointment please reply with', 'phone number', '#of adults', '#of children', '# & breed of any pets', 'Home normally rents for $1400 but the price was reduced to insure its rented 9/1.', 'Lock in to the low rate of $1275 per month if you move in by 9/1.', 'LIMIT OF NO MORE THAN 3 OCCUPANTS', 'BE SURE TO INCLUDE A PHONE# PLEASE', "It's CUTE", "but it's SMALL 900 Sq feet", 'Washer yes', 'Dryer yes', 'Dishwasher yes', 'Ac yes', 'HWF in living room yes', 'Carpeted bedrooms yes', 'Off street parking yes', 'FREE TO APPLY!!', 'Please include phone number, #of adults, #of children, & # & type of any pets', 'Certain pets OK with pet deposit.', 'Tenants pay all utilities.', 'Must have clean rental history', '-NO EVICTIONS / UDS ON RECORD!', 'No emergency assistance applications.', 'Not section 8', 'Include phone number, #of adults, #of children, & # & type of any pets', 'If you are unwilling or unable to provide a phone # please do not reply']
